      "Bash(~/.claude/skills/gstack/bin/gstack-learnings-log '{\"skill\":\"qa-only\",\"type\":\"pitfall\",\"key\":\"antd_otp_not_fillable\",\"insight\":\"Antd OTP .ant-otp component \\(6 inputs maxlength=1\\) cannot be filled via Playwright fill/click/press or JS nativeInputValueSetter — React controlled state does not sync. Backend rejects OTP as wrong/expired. Workaround: request dev team add OTP bypass env var \\(TEST_OTP_BYPASS=true + magic code 666666\\).\",\"confidence\":9,\"source\":\"observed\",\"files\":[\"output/qa-reports/round1/permission-matrix-module2/permission-matrix-test-report.md\"]}')",
